{"tid":614491,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[TG谷] 孤兒瘋人院","createTime":"2018-04-02T14:42:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-24T17:35:01.000Z","uid":171592,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"630e8526967b7e43ff2aef2a3969ef5f35e91963","tid":614491,"uid":171592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T14:42:42.000Z","msg":"孤兒瘋人院   <br />\n專收集一堆說話太瘋癲而被踢或者鍾意玩狼人既孤兒，隨意傾談你既所思所想,<br />\n以下人士請勿內進:<br />\n- 23歲以下人士  <br />\n- 搵食人士即踢   <br />\n- 狗公麻煩走啦    <br />\n- 娘娘行遠啲呀  <br />\n<br />\n我地谷內已有專屬狗公、娘娘、搵食人士，佢地會不斷監察，以防有人威脅到佢地既地位。 <br />\n每個月會清一次深潛人士，拒絕cdrom，大家有心想傾計先入，谷內有來自各行各業既人，想傾乜都可以，只怕你開唔到題。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/DzuS7EnAjDZj0wyN-zIbdg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FDzuS7EnAjDZj0wyN-zIbdg&d=6NjUVdMNZjxvOCxuEg%2FSzIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=65d74c56\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/DzuS7EnAjDZj0wyN-zIbdg</a>"},{"pid":"d75ca733cd3f782e6eda4bd90b121afcd8fbe4c5","tid":614491,"uid":171592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T11:48:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"079a80cf1c8983e851fd0a843950b607292a57f5","tid":614491,"uid":171592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T14:50:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7d0dc424083dbc1488727f6fda753aee7ba628d","tid":614491,"uid":79233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T17:35:01.000Z","msg":"想請問版主, 若被 Bam! 後既朋友能否有機會請版主作 Un-bam 呢?<br />\n<br />\n同時:<br />\n<br />\n1: 原想像 HKG 內的 PM [留言] 直接給版主, 但後來先發覺原來兩個 Forum 有咁樣既<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"></span>差別。<br />\n2: 假如版主方便的話, 可以留 TG 內的 User ID (稱謂) 作聯絡呢? 望版大能回覆在下問題, 謝謝!"}]}